features: 【Cute Spring Home Decor Aesthetic】Colourful flower bee tulip and cornflower Spring decor throw pillow covers. You can't miss them! And if you give them as a gift, you'll receive lots of compliments from neighbours and friends. This versatile floral pillow cover set has you covered!

【Indoor & Outdoor Decorations】These pretty floral Spring pillow covers are perfect for decorating Outdoor Garden Bench Veranda Porch Swing Balcony Rocking chair and etc. Also suitable for Indoors: Bed, Sofa, Couch, Living Room, Bedroom and etc. (Of course they are not waterproof).
【No Pillow Inserts】 Set of 2 Spring lumbar pillow covers without pillow inserts. Each measures about 12 x 20 inches. As they are hand-cut and sewn, please allow a 0.5 inch deviation in size.

【Good Workmanship】 These Spring and Summer seasonl outdoor decorative lumbar pillow covers are made of premium polyester and linen blend fabric (Soft Burlap Fabric Like). A little rough to the touch but won't hurt your skin. Thick enough to cover any colored pillow inserts, great living room decor for the whole spring and summer season. The material isn't particularly soft, but it's durable, the patterns are bright and vivid, and it's easy to clean.

【Hidden Zipper】 The farmhouse Spring lumbar pillow covers has an invisible zipper at the bottom, making it effort less to fill or remove the pillow cover while ensuring the aesthetics of the pillow. Although the edges of the zipper are reinforced with stitching, please still do not tear the pillowcase with force.
【Not White Pillow Covers】 The cute flower patterns are printed on one side only, the back is a solid beige (sand) colour, not white.
【Wash and Care】 Handwash or machine wash in cold water separately. Gently cycle only and do not bleach or tumble dry. Do not iron.
body.description: Update your home decor with these JOJOGOGO Spring Flower pillow covers.Made of 80% polyester and 20% linen, comfortable and breathable.Invisible zipper allows the inserts can be inserted and removed from the covers easily.No Pillow Inserts!Suitable for bedroom, living room, dining room, bed, sofa, couch.It can also be used as a gift for relatives, friends and neighbors.Hand wash or machine wash separately in cold water on the gentle cycle, tumble dry low, do not bleach.
